### ===========================
### Saga Monitor API - REST Client
### ===========================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3100/v1

### ----- SAGAS -----

### List all sagas
GET {{baseUrl}}/sagas

### List sagas with filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/sagas?status=RUNNING&limit=10

### List sagas by name
GET {{baseUrl}}/sagas?sagaName=RecurringPaymentSaga&limit=20

### List sagas by root ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/sagas?sagaRootId={{rootId}}&limit=20

### List COMPENSATING sagas
GET {{baseUrl}}/sagas?status=COMPENSATING

### List COMPLETED sagas
GET {{baseUrl}}/sagas?status=COMPLETED&limit=50

### List sagas with cursor pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/sagas?limit=5&cursor={{sagaId}}

### ----- SAGA DETAIL -----

### Get saga detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/sagas/{{sagaId}}

### ----- SAGA EVENTS (TIMELINE) -----

### Get saga event timeline
GET {{baseUrl}}/sagas/{{sagaId}}/events

### Get saga events with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/sagas/{{sagaId}}/events?limit=10

### Get saga events with cursor
GET {{baseUrl}}/sagas/{{sagaId}}/events?limit=10&cursor={{eventId}}

### ----- SAGA TREE -----

### Get saga tree by root ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/sagas/root/{{rootId}}

### ----- SAGA METRICS -----

### Get saga execution metrics
GET {{baseUrl}}/sagas/{{sagaId}}/metrics

### ----- SSE STREAMS -----

### Stream all saga updates (SSE)
GET {{baseUrl}}/stream/sagas
Accept: text/event-stream

### Stream updates for a specific saga (SSE)
GET {{baseUrl}}/stream/sagas/{{sagaId}}
Accept: text/event-stream

### Stream updates for a saga root tree (SSE)
GET {{baseUrl}}/stream/sagas/root/{{rootId}}
Accept: text/event-stream

### ----- SWAGGER -----

### Open Swagger UI
GET http://localhost:3100/api
